quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  14,1,"Alô. Tazmamt, Nessers ak p id, iwakken a ppessuff$ev imdanen si tillas ar tafat, s wannuf n Mass nnsen, s abrid n Wuzmir, Amaâzuz"
  14,2,"Öebbi ilan i illan deg igenwan, i illan di tmurt. A ssxev ijehliyen, ilmend uâaqeb uqsiê"
  14,3,"i ismenyafen tameddurt n ddunit wala laxeôt, i iswexxiôen seg ubrid n Öebbi, u ssaramen t d uâwij! Widak, atnan di ttelfan u$miq"
  14,4,"Ur d Nuzen amazan, siwa s tmeslayt n ugdud is, iwakken ad asen ibeggen. Öebbi Itellif win i S ihwan, Inehhu win i S ihwan. Neppa d Uzmir, d Bab n ûûwab"
  14,5,"Ih, ni$ Nuzen ed Musa, s issekniyen nne£: \"ssuffe$ agdud ik, si tillas ar tafat. Mmekti yas d ussan n Öebbi\". Deg waya, war ccekk, d issekniyen i yal aûebôi isnemmiren"
  14,6,"Mi inna Musa i ugdud is: \"mmektit ed l$it ikwen I$at Öebbi, mi kwen Isellek si lois n Ferâun, i issuken fellawen lhemm uqsiê. Zellun arrac nnwen, ssidiren tilawin nnwen. Deg waya, s$uô Mass nnwen, d cedda tameqwôaêant"